{"tid":1955180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港電台回應表示並無違反「一國兩制」及《香港電台約章》","createTime":"2020-04-02T10:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T10:32:21.000Z","uid":25240,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bf29029946c9ecb611166387dd9ccd9d09586125","tid":1955180,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:23:15.000Z","msg":"香港電台回應 #ThePulse<br />\n<br />\n就 2020 年 3 月 28 日英文節目《脈搏》（The Pulse），香港電台發言人回應如下：　<br />\n<br />\n當天播出之《脈搏》，主題是探討世界各地新冠肺炎疫情，以歐洲、美洲疫情最嚴重的城市為切入點，如紐約、倫敦、以至意大利北部最受影響的倫巴第大區。該集旨在分析各地疫情之應對及受影響的民眾感受，有各地方政府的說法，亦有世衞的回應。<br />\n<br />\n當提及台灣，節目只以地方（place)來形容，本身並沒有任何取態。<br />\n<br />\n香港電台審視全集內容後，認為該集節目並無違反「一國兩制」，亦沒有違反《香港電台約章》。<br />\n<br />\n#ThePulse #電視部公共事務組 #WHO<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/565309940283256/posts/1585783061569267/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F565309940283256%2Fposts%2F1585783061569267%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=9a470d0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/565309940283256/posts/1585783061569267/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"9e07d315e275a12367f564867058da21baf94eb1","tid":1955180,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:24:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc85d55225959952288f8749c6f197b42c2acba8","tid":1955180,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc69804b539148e4c6b81eef7a5607687096a45","tid":1955180,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:26:03.000Z","msg":"快d 幫手cls"},{"pid":"cfb2865c46b381e204f575aa0fc9bd1d1a4dcf70","tid":1955180,"uid":70342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:26:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02304c69c68214246a37cd0cee8431127409ddea","tid":1955180,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:27:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598c0b2636d5161d2da032df93797f021e8e12cc","tid":1955180,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:27:51.000Z","msg":"本來唔知, 原來台灣係有分別"},{"pid":"16b8ed97aaed882ed64a7c4a03cefbe529c780c3","tid":1955180,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:32:21.000Z","msg":"大家一齊send email去商經局同廣播處長支持Rthk<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=124282159188978&amp;id=104015014549026\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D124282159188978%26id%3D104015014549026&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=8b86ff66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=124282159188978&amp;id=104015014549026</a>"}]}